  (text "Key Jetson carrier board requirements:\n• 5V @ 5A minimum on pin groups (clean, low noise)\n• POWER_EN: assert after 5V stable (100ms delay suggested)\n• USB-C on J13 → Jetson USB for flashing (via USB_D+/D- passthrough)\n• CSI camera on J3 (22-pin FPC, 2-lane MIPI)\n• Ethernet: optional — use USB3 dongle if not routing RTL8153\n• Recovery button + Force Recovery GPIO required"
